### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### 2. Create Pet (LLM1 initial profile)
POST http://localhost:8080/pets
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ポチ",
  "personality": "好奇心旺盛で探検家みたい",
  "tone": "やわらかく短文、断定しない"
}

###

### 3. Submit Input - public (LLM1 classification)
POST http://localhost:8080/inputs
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input_type": "chat",
  "content": "最近カフェで作業するのにはまってる。特に朝の静かな時間帯が好き"
}

###

### 4. Submit Input - should be blocked (PII)
POST http://localhost:8080/inputs
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input_type": "chat",
  "content": "私の電話番号は090-1234-5678です"
}

###

### 5. Get Public Memory
GET http://localhost:8080/memories/public
Authorization: Bearer dev-token

###

### 6. Get Review Items
GET http://localhost:8080/memories/review
Authorization: Bearer dev-token

###

### 7. Approve Review Item
PUT http://localhost:8080/memories/ITEM_ID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "approve"
}

###

### 8. Issue Exchange Token
POST http://localhost:8080/exchanges/token
Authorization: Bearer dev-token

###

### 9. Join Exchange (use token from step 8)
POST http://localhost:8080/exchanges/join
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "TOKEN_FROM_STEP_8",
  "exchange_method": "qr_fallback"
}

###

### 10. Approve Exchange (user A - session from step 9)
POST http://localhost:8080/exchanges/SESSION_ID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}

###

### 11. Get Analysis (LLM2 result)
GET http://localhost:8080/exchanges/SESSION_ID_HERE/analysis
Authorization: Bearer dev-token

###

### 12. Get Post-Visit Report (LLM3 - lazy generation)
GET http://localhost:8080/reports/ANALYSIS_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer dev-token

###

### 13. Submit Feedback (LLM4 memory update)
POST http://localhost:8080/reports/ANALYSIS_ID_HERE/feedback
Authorization: Bearer dev-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "card_id": "CARD_ID_HERE",
  "reaction": "saved"
}
